---
import EmailReport from './product/EmailReport.astro';
---

<section id="report" class="section section-y bg-cream-200/40">
  <div class="container-page">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
      <div class="lg:col-span-5">
        <p class="eyebrow">After every session</p>
        <h2 class="mt-4 font-serif text-display-2 text-ink-900 leading-[1.05]">
          A thoughtful email
          after every <span class="accent-italic">session</span>.
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-ink-600 text-[16.5px] leading-[1.65] max-w-[44ch]">
          Every Siko session ends with an honest email to whoever&rsquo;s on the
          report list &mdash; your own address for self-tracking, a parent&rsquo;s for
          observability, or both. It says, specifically, what got worked on
          and where things got stuck.
        </p>

        <dl class="mt-9 space-y-6 max-w-[42ch]">
          <div>
            <dt class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-eyebrow text-gold-400 mb-1.5">Honest</dt>
            <dd class="text-ink-700 text-[15px] leading-[1.6]">
              We never invent metrics. The numbers in the email are counted
              directly from the session, not guessed.
            </dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-eyebrow text-gold-400 mb-1.5">Specific</dt>
            <dd class="text-ink-700 text-[15px] leading-[1.6]">
              &ldquo;Got stuck distributing the 5 across <em>(x &minus; 2)</em>&rdquo; &mdash;
              not &ldquo;had trouble with math.&rdquo;
            </dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-eyebrow text-gold-400 mb-1.5">Calibrated</dt>
            <dd class="text-ink-700 text-[15px] leading-[1.6]">
              The tone shifts based on what actually happened &mdash;
              encouraging, neutral, or concerned. Never pathologizing.
            </dd>
          </div>
        </dl>

        <p class="mt-10 pl-5 border-l-2 border-gold-300 text-ink-700 text-[15px] leading-[1.65] italic max-w-[44ch] font-serif" style="font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 14;">
          &ldquo;Siko refuses to give answers &mdash; every hint above is a Socratic
          question or nudge that asks the student to do the thinking.&rdquo;
          <span class="block mt-2 not-italic font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-eyebrow text-ink-500">
            &mdash; the footer on every email Siko sends
          </span>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-7">
        <EmailReport />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
